lyrics:
[Verse]
Rain starts pouring, it's a wet surprise
At the park, kids playing, dark clouds arise
Gotta pack up, can't stay any longer
Mood's getting gloomy, but we'll be stronger

[Chorus]
In the British rain, we'll find our way
Together we'll dance, make our spirits sway
Though we leave the park, we won't lose our spark
In the British rain, we'll make our mark
